Text: PIN Request for Gold PassportMR SHAPIRO Thank you for your recent inquiry regarding your Gold Passport Personal Identification Number Your PIN is Your PIN allows you to have secured access to your account activity and update your account information hours a day seven days a week To use your PIN just visit our web site at wwwgoldpassportcom or call Gold Passports Automated Information Line at HYATT or outside the US and Canada If you prefer a different PIN you can change it by visiting wwwGoldpassportcom or calling the Automated Account Information Line If you have any questions regarding your Gold Passport PIN please feel fre e to contact us Thank you for choosing Hyatt With Gold Passport Membership Makes A World of Difference Sincerely Gold Passport Customer Service Where to Write Or Call Within the US or Canada call for reservations for Automated Account Information call HYATT Outside the US or Canada call fax or call your nearest Hyatt Worldwide Reservation Centre Australia toll free Germany Hong Kong Indonesia Japan Korea Mexico toll free Singapore Taiwan United Kingdom US Canada toll free HYATT Hyatt Gold Passport Customer Service Center POBox Omaha NE USA Or visit wwwgoldpassportcom
